---
title: Pork Sausage & Caramelised Onion Pie with Lemony Veggies
description: You can’t beat a classic... but you can certainly twist it around and create something equally great. This sausage and caramelised onion pie is a prime example – tasty sausages in a sweet onion gravy are topped with grilled mashed potato and paired with a side of citrusy veggies. It's old-school and it's downright delicious!
